<br>
For a bogus statistical sample: <br>
Looking at a fairly wordy page of Blade of the Immortal I counted: 40 kanji, 15 katakana and 108 hiragana.<br>
<br>
Looking at one paragraph of that newspaper article: 73 kanji, 7 katakana, 34 hiragana.<br>
<br>
See what I mean? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uthaumivore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>thaumivore</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/18/02 8:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=655.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/thaumivore/face.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re: questions</span><hr size=1> cool, thanks.<br>
